title: Asking for help identifying this face
content:
I've exhausted all the usual suspects on this and still can't nail it down. Does it look familiar to you? Can you guide me to it? The example is on this site

[http://www.vivandlarry.com/?cat=841](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415130454/http:/www.vivandlarry.com/?cat=841 "http://www.vivandlarry.com/?cat=841")

It's the font used for the aqua titles and in the logo. I've attached a .jpg of some key caps in the font.

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415130454im_/http:/typophile.com/files/Untitled-1_5460.jpg)

Thank you so much for reading my post and offering any help you might be able to give me.
author: MS47
